<title>
Kontrola systému zavesenia
</title>
<ptxt>
Nadvihnite vozidlo a skontrolujte nasledovné časti. Dotiahnite, opravte alebo vymeňte za nové, ak sú poškodené.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
<emph>
Predné zavesenie
</emph>
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Rám predného zavesenia: 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "ASLAP70A2206015"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Rameno zavesenia kolesa: 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "ASLAP70A2206009"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Predná montážna zostava vzpery: 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "ASLAP70A2206005"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Kontrola vinutej pružiny, ložiska vzpery a podpery vzpery: 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "ASLAP70A2206006"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Tyč a kĺb predného stabilizátora: 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "ASLAP70A2206016"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A210001.jpg" width = "88.000mm" height = "102.654mm" ver = "01" gw = "206" gh = "274"/>
</figure>
<ptxt>
<emph>
Zadné pruženie
</emph>
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Zadná náprava: 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "ASLAP70A2306008"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Zadný tlmič odpruženia: 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "ASLAP70A2306004"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Zadná vinutá pružina: 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "ASLAP70A2306006"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
